  Mummy:

    Whenever a contact move hits 
  this Pokémon, the attacking Pokémon's 
  ability changes to Mummy.

  multitype is unaffected. If 
  a Pokémon with moxie knocks this 
  Pokémon out, the former's ability 
  will change without taking effect.


